column7: Thomas & Friends Toy Train  Set with Motorized Toy Train
column8:
Get ready for a fun-filled Thomas & Friends delivery adventure at the Dieselworks with Diesels Lift & Shift Set from Fisher-Price! Start by picking up the oil drum from the barrel loader. You can use the stop-track to stop Diesel in front, then tip the loader so the barrel rolls into his cargo car. With his cargo in tow, Diesel speeds ahead to the fueling station, where you can push the fuel nozzle down to stop him, and move the nozzle up to send him on his way. Next, when he races into the Dieselworks, the engine hoist lifts him and his cargo car, then amazingly transfers them to the other track! With a full track layout, two stop-tracks, and cool engine-lifting action, Diesels Lift & Shift Set helps you create a world of imaginative play while expanding your Thomas & Friends Motorized Railway! Children ages 3Y+.

Start Thomas near the yellow signal gantry and send him through the caution signs towards the shipwreck. As Thomas crosses the ship, the deck collapses and the big pirate flag pops up while a secret passage is revealed in the hull of the shipwreck! Below deck, Thomas pushes Skiff the rail-boat out from the bow towards Knapford Station. When Skiff enters the station, Sailor John pops out from behind the door and the treasure suddenly appears in Skiffs stern! With the treasure, Thomas and Skiff race over the hill to the harbor, and as they crash into the water, the waves splash up around them! Use the directional switch to send them through the hull of the ship, or back up over the deck! Full of fun characters and thrilling action, Thomas Shipwreck Adventure brings the world of Thomas & Friends to life! Children ages 3Y+.

column7: Three levels of play with songs, phrases & sounds for your childs age & stage!
column8:
Its babys very own place to sit and discover new thingsincluding ABCs, 1-2-3s, colors, shapes, and more! The magic seat knows whenever baby sits down or stands up, and it rewards baby with songs and phrases every time. Baby can also press the light-up remote or flip the book pages to hear over 50 sing-along songs, tunes and phrasesand lift seat cushion to find even more fun surprises underneath!

Smart Stages Chair includes Smart Stages technology, an exciting new way to change learning content as baby grows. Every baby develops at their own pace, and Smart Stages technology gives you the ability to select the stage thats best for your child! There are a variety of developmentally appropriate songs, phrases and sounds within three levels of playjust slide the switch, or enter babys age for automatic level changes.

Smart Stages Technology
Level 1 Explore 12M+
First words and sounds spark babys curiosity
Level 2 Encourage 18M+
Prompt baby though questions and simple directions
Level 3 Pretend 24M+
Imaginative fun and early role play

Features
50+ sing-along songs, tunes & phrases
Includes Smart Stages technology learning content changes as baby grows
Three levels of play offer fresh songs, phrases & sounds for your little ones age & stage
Enter babys age for automatic Smart Stages level changes or manually change levels with the switch
Seat activates songs & phrases when baby sits & stands
Busy activities include an illustrated flip-book & light-up remote control with buttons to press
Lift the seat for fun surprises
Teaches first words, numbers, shapes, colors and more
Requires 3 AA batteries

Toddlers will be so busy scooping, squirting and pouring, theyll never want to get out of the tub! (But when they do, everything drains and stores right on the bath bar until next time)

Includes 3 adorable friends: scoop-and-strain fish, spinning starfish & squirting whale
3 removable fill-and-pour activities for nearly endless ways to play!
Suctions to tub stays put for play
Toys attach easily and securely to bar for easy draining and storage

column7: Water-blasting fire boat helps kids save the day!
column8:
When theres a water rescue to be made or a harbor fire to fight, the City Firefighting Boat is ready to help! Kids turn on the adventure when they put the firefighting figure on the disk and turn him to rotate the water cannonsthen submerge the boat in water, pump to fill the cannons, and press the disk to squirt water. column8:
Thomas & Friends Collectible Mini Toy Train in Single Blind Pack

Thomas & Friends engines just got a mini makeover! With over 70 mini engines to collect, Thomas & Friends Minis from Fisher-Price completely reimagine the Island of Sodor with never-before-seen themes! From Spooky monsters and speedy Racers, to super-themed Heroes and prehistoric Dino engines, this collection of pintsized engines showcases Thomas & Friends in a whole new way! Of course, no collection is complete without your favorite characters in their classic styles, which is why Thomas & Friends Minis also include 30 classic engines in addition to over 40 themed engines.

This single blind pack contains one mystery character! After all, with a variety of unique engines to collect some rarer than others half the fun is guessing whos hiding inside! Collect em, race em, trade em, and use your imagination to create really unique adventures for these Really Useful engines!

Features
Single blind pack contains one mystery Thomas & Friends character
Over 70 Thomas & Friends Minis to collect
Never-before-seen themes and styles
Look for more characters and themes as theyre introduced

Thomas & Friends Collectible Mini Toy Train in Single Blind Pack

Thomas & Friends engines just got a mini makeover! With over 70 mini engines to collect, Thomas & Friends Minis from Fisher-Price completely reimagine the Island of Sodor with never-before-seen themes! From Spooky monsters and speedy Racers, to super-themed Heroes and prehistoric Dino engines, this collection of pintsized engines showcases Thomas & Friends in a whole new way! Of course, no collection is complete without your favorite characters in their classic styles, which is why Thomas & Friends Minis also include 30 classic engines in addition to over 40 themed engines.

This single blind pack contains one mystery character! After all, with a variety of unique engines to collect some rarer than others half the fun is guessing whos hiding inside! Collect em, race em, trade em, and use your imagination to create really unique adventures for these Really Useful engines!

Features
Single blind pack contains one mystery Thomas & Friends character
Over 70 Thomas & Friends Minis to collect
Never-before-seen themes and styles
Look for more characters and themes as theyre introduced

Age Grade - 3Y+

column6: My Little Snugabear Ballerina Cradle n Swing
column7: Soothing baby swing swings 2 ways: rocks side-to-side like a cradle & swings head-to-toe!
column8:
Deluxe baby swing features and pink/grey fabrics make Fisher-Price My Little Snugabear Ballerina Cradle n Swing soft and soothingjust like a little bear hug!with two different swinging motions and a variety of other customizable features that let you choose and combine what baby likes best! SmartSwing Technology offers six different baby swing speeds from low to highwhether baby is rocking side-to-side, or swinging head-to-toe. Its easy to switch from one swing motion to another; just push a button and turn the seat! My Little Snugabear cradle swing actually senses babys weight, so speeds wont slow as baby grows, and it starts without a push. The motorized mobile helps soothe baby, too, with 16 songs, nature sounds and three adorable ballerina bear friends that dance overhead to encourage eye-tracking and keep baby entertained. And the mirrored globe in the center of the mobile lets baby see all around the room! The deep, cozy seat with machine-washable padded seat cover has a linkable rattle toy, and a machine-washable body insert and head support for newborns, infants and smaller babies. My Little Snugabear Cradle n Swing is easy to assemble, with legs that fold for storage or portable room-to-room use. Two convenient power options make My Little Snugabear Cradle n Swing easy to use anywhere around the house. Plug it in for battery-free baby swing operation when youre near an outlet, or switch to battery power swinging when youre not!

Features
Two swing motions to help soothe baby: rock baby side-to-side like a cradle or swing head-to-toe
Fisher-Price SmartSwing Technology
Six swing speeds, 16 songs, soothing nature sounds
Motorized mobile with mirrored globe and three ballerina bear mobile toys
Two-position recline with 3 adjustable seat positions: right-facing, center, left-facing
Easy to convert to different positionsjust press button and turn
Deep & cozy Papasan-style seat
Machine-washable seat cover with deluxe My Little Snugabear body insert and head support
Plush, snuggly fabrics with airy canopy
Linkable rattle toy detaches for take along
Easy to assemble
Legs fold for storage and portable room-to-room use
Two power options: plug in or battery-powered
Includes AC adapter or requires 4 D alkaline batteries

Maximum Weightt: 25 lbs. (11,3 kg)

Developmental Guidelines Use from birth until child attempts to climb out of product.

column7: Lights, sounds, music, Rainforest Friends toysand tons of jumping fun!
column8:
More bouncy, jumping, motor-skill-building Jumperoo fun for baby than everin a portable, height-adjustable, space saving design! Babys favorite Fisher-Price Rainforest Friends are ready to play on the soft-sided activity toy archwith even more sensory-stimulating activity toy play right at babys fingertips. Theres a colorful, light-up rainbow-key piano to play, a bobble frog teether to chew on, a clacker ring bar to slide 3 colorful rings back and forth, and a turtle to click-click-click! And thats not all! Babys natural jumping and kicking actions send the seat bouncing up and down for a really fun and exciting ride and babys jumping is rewarded with lights, sounds and music! The sturdy Jumperoo frame is free-standing for convenience (it wont block a doorway!), height-adjustable (so it grows with baby!), and its easy to fold flat for portability and space saving storage (with the removable toy bar stored flat, too!). The bouncy spring is in the back, enclosed in a soft-fabric cover and out of babys reach, and the soft, padded fabric seat cover removes for machine washing.

column6: 4-in-1 Rock n Glide Soother - Coastal Mist
column7: Help soothe baby with a gentle rock or glide, head-to-toe or side-to-side!
column8:
Most babies love the soothing comfort and motion of being rocked and cradled in moms arms. Thats why, with 4 soothing rock and glide motions, calming vibrations, and a soft, padded seat, Fisher-Price 4-in-1 Rock n Glide Soother was designed to mimic the soothing motion and comfort of baby being cradled, rocked, and soothed. Its actually two babygear must-haves in onewith four different ways to move (and help soothe) baby! Baby can rock or glide head-to-toe or side-to-side, with optional, battery-powered calming vibrations. Just choose rock or glide mode, then turn the rock & glide seat to select head-to-toe or side-to-side motion. (The seat rotates 360 degrees, so its easy to keep baby in sight!) Convenient foot pedal operation lets you quickly turn AC-powered gliding motion on or off; music and nature sounds help soothe and comfort baby, too! Its quick and easy to convert 4-in-1 Rock n Glide Soother from a powered glider to a cozy cradle rockerjust lift the calming vibrations rocker seat from the glider base. The portable seat with removable newborn head and body support insert adjusts to 2 different rock n glide positions, so it grows with baby from newborn, to infant, to older baby. Choose reclined for newborns, infants, and soothing or napping; or inclined for older babies and play time! The removable toy bar keeps baby entertained with two soft toys overhead, with a linkable fox blankie with satin-tipped tail for hands-on fun, too!

Features
Four different rock n glide motions help soothe baby
Rocks or glides head-to-toe or side-to-side
Three gliding speeds and two reclining positions
Calming vibrations
12 songs & 3 soothing nature sound effects
Seat easily removes to go from glider to rocker
Removable toy bar with soft fox toys keeps baby entertained
Linkable fox blankie with satin-tipped tail
Machine-washable soft-fabric seat pad and infant body & head support
Seat handles for easy room-to-room portability
Easy to assemble
Includes AC adapter for glider
Requires 1 D battery for calming vibrations

Age Grade Maximum weight: 25 lbs (11,3 kg)

Developmental Statement Use from birth until child is able to sit up unassisted.

column7: Three grow-with-me stages let kids rock, roll, and ride from as young as 1all the way to 5!
column8:
The youngest of riders can enjoy indoor/outdoor fun on the stationary rocker base. When theyre ready to roll, its quick and easy to remove and convert the base into an extra-long push handle for parents. Before they can pedal, toddlers can learn to steer as you help them roll along! Then, when theyre ready for big-kid pedaling fun, simply remove the handle, fold-up the footrest, and theyre offwith durable tires, easy-grip handlebars, chunky foot pedals and an adjustable grow-with-me seat. Trike easily converts from one stage to another and back again, no tools required.

Three grow-with-me stages let kids Rock, Roll, and Ride!

Easy to convertno tools required.

column6: Ultra-Lite Day & Night Play Yard - Morning Cloud
column7: The ultra-lite, portable play yard that weighs just 15 lbs!
column8:
Take some weight off your shoulders with a portable play yard thats just half the weight of other popular play yards, with all the same great features, and more.

Its everything you and baby need to play, sleep, change and repeat at home or on the go! At only 15 lbs, its super lightweight and easy-peasy to take down, pop up and pack away in just a few quick, simple steps. A supportive seat back, cushioned head support and three-point restraint keep baby comfy in the inclined sleeper the way lots of babies sleep best.

Remove the sleeper and it becomes a roomy space for older babies and toddlers to rest, relax and play. Too-good-to-be-true details include a padded platform that fits any standard-size crib sheet and a built-in play yard storage pocket that holds a portable changing station diaper clutchgreat for quick and easy diaper changes at home, or on the go. Plenty of room to BYO diapers!

The Ultra-Lite Day & Night Play Yard is a night saver and a life saver.

Inclined sleeper, changing station and play yard in one
Only 15 lbs--half the weight of other portable play yards
Removable inclined sleeper with machine-washable pad and head support
Portable changing station diaper clutch with built in wipes container
Comfortable padded play yard mat
Easy to assemble
Easy to foldno loose pieces
Carry bag for easy , hands-free carry and storage

Age Grade Birth +

Developmental Guidelines Use play yard with a child who cannot climb out and is less than 35 inches in height. Use inclined sleeper only with a child unable to sit up unassisted or grasp side of seat and pull upward.

Soft, cuddly Kira introduces baby to music, the alphabet, numbers, colors and more in both Spanish and English! Features 2 modes: Music and Learning and 3 activation points: 2 paws and her heart. Kiras heart even lights up and dances to the music! Shes the purr-fect pal for giving baby a sense of happiness & security and teaching baby important concepts mostly through sung songs and music!

When it comes to babys development, the early years are the most important. Each play experience is an opportunity for baby to explore the world around them, taking it all in, learning, doing, and discovering new things along the way. The Shakira First Steps Collection encourages babys well-rounded development, helping baby get ready for their first steps and beyond!

Features
Plush character provides bilingual, sing-along fun and learning content, too!
2 modes: Music and Learning with Spanish incorporated into both modes
3 activation points:
ABC Paw Kira introduces babys favorite melodies in Music Mode and teaches ABCs, 123s, and colors in Learning Mode
Games Paw Kira plays peek-a-boo with baby in Music Mode and encourages baby to get up and move in Learning Mode
Heart Kira loves her friends and wants to teach baby all about proper manners and friendship!
Introduces early learning concepts to baby
By pressing Kiras paws & heart to hear fun phrases & music, babys learning that their actions make exciting things happen!

There are a variety of developmentally appropriate songs, phrases and sounds within three levels of play.

Just add sand, dirt and a little imagination and kids will love digging up lots of new adventures catching crabs and who knows what else! ImaginextTurn on Adventure!

column8:
Get ready for more Octonauts adventures with the Gup-I Transforming Polar Vehicle!

The Gup-I is inspired by the durability and adaptability of the water bear. Part polar exploration station and part rugged vehicle, this Gup-I is equipped with everything the Octonauts need for creature rescues despite the worst of weather conditions. This transforming Gup features 3 ways to play! In Water Bear Mode, the Gup-I is in a horizontal position, allowing the Octonauts to explore or race to the rescue! In Scout Mode, the Gup-I can stand upright, giving the team the perfect view to scan and spot creatures from afar. In Command Center Mode, the Gup-I opens to reveal everything the Octonauts need for their rescues! The Gup-I comes with Kwazii in his snowsuit, an Adelie penguin to rescue and a satellite dish play piece. Not intended for water play. 3+

column7: Recreate the Rapunzel fairy tale with this magical tower playset, featuring climbing basket with trap door, hair elevator and rocking boat.

Will they let Flynn Rider climb Rapunzels locks to rescue her from the tower to live happily ever after? Or will they press the basket to send him flying through the trap door before he can reach his princess? column6: Disney Captain Jake and the Never Land Pirates - Key to the Sea Battle Adventure
column8:
Captain Jakes trusty skiff is newly equipped with a secret skull key feature that can only be unlocked by whoever possesses the golden key.

Now that Jakes been promoted to Captain hes ready to set sail on a whole new adventure, so he needs a brand new skiff. Captain Jakes trusty new skiff has been equipped with a new secret skull key feature that can only be unlocked by the person who possesses the secret golden skull key. With his new skeleton key in hand, Captain Jake can turn the main sail of his ship and unlock a new secret adventure. X unlocks the spot as you insert the key into the top of Buckys crows nest and twist. As you turn the key, the mast pivots and unlocks the secret plank that slides out, revealing Captain Jakes hidden treasure. But what if the ship comes under attack by Captain Hook? Captain Jakes new battle ship also comes equipped with a cannon that launches anchor-shaped projectiles to keep the pirate baddies at bay. Youll control the key to the sea as you use the secret golden key to unlock Captain Jakes newest pirate adventure. column7: Give these fun characters a spin, with gravity-defying action to amaze little ones!
column8:
What are YOs and what makes them go? Theyre cool, round things that love to spin fast, and love to spin slow. How do they stay on track? kids ask as they play. Its magic of course! (Thats what you should say.) Just place one or both YOs on the track piece. Then take the YOs for a ridemake em slide go upside down and round & round & round! Its a whole new spin on defying gravity! Theres a crazy character on one side of each YO, and a cool visual effect on the other side. The track piece easily attaches to sections of the Spinnyos Giant YO-ller Coaster set for more spin-tacular fun! (Coaster sold separately.)

How do YOs stay on the track? Well, it seems like magic, but actually theres a kid-safe magnetic axle inside the YOs spinners that attaches to the metallic edge on the track. Theyre so much fun that once kids start spinning em, they wont want to stop! (You wont either try em and see for yourself!) Theyre YO-tally awesome!

Place the Spinnyos YOs on the track piece and move it in any direction to send the YOs spinning up, down and all around!
Wacky character on one side, cool visual effect on the other

column8:
Since the 1920s, ice cream trucks have filled the air with sweet, familiar melodies. From local neighborhoods to beaches and parks, these musical vehicles offer more than sugary treatsthey deliver the sounds of summer. Now children can create their own musical melodies with the Sweet Sounds Ice Cream Truck from Fisher-Price Wooden Toys, an heirloom-quality toy truck delivering fun-filled play that can help promote early childhood development. As children use the mallet to play the chimes, theyre exercising fine motor skills and imagination while expressing themselves creatively. Ringing the bell also promotes curiosity and logical thinking as they discover what mechanisms produce fun, exciting sounds.

Plus, pushing and rolling the truck along can also help encourage gross motor skills through physical play. This musical vehicle is meticulously constructed using real beech wood and stylishly designed to offer a stimulating sensory experience with engaging colors, appealing textures, and charming sounds. Explore the endless potential of a childs imagination, and share the musical journey with the Sweet Sounds Ice Cream Truck from Fisher-Price.

column7: Designed to help children develop through fun, beneficial play, this unique set of wooden toys and accessories lets toddlers mix, match, stack, and create their own original totem towers.
column8:
Totem poles are sculptures carved on tall, wooden posts, some of which can reach over sixty feet (18 meters) tall. Although toddlers may not be able to stack these wooden toys quite so high, theyll love using fine motor skills to connect them, and imagination and creativity to rearrange their unique accessories. These artfully crafted Totem Pole Pals, from the Fisher-Price Wooden Toys collection, are made with real beech wood and designed to be equally beneficial, eye-catching, and engaging.

Each wooden piece features different faces and expressions, along with bristles that allow for easy connection to the other pieces in the set. Plus, the circular faces can rotate between the bristles, so toddlers can spin them to see the varying expressions. As children build their totem towers, they can use the adorable, interchangeable accessories to customize them. With fun decorations like a hat, moustache, bowtie, lips, glasses and bunny ears, toddlers can create original combinations that reflect a variety of characteristics, personalities, emotions, and expressions. As children stack them up, up, up, their smiles will grow, grow, grow. You can even call these tactical totems mood elevators. (See what we did there?)

Set includes 7 accessories and 6 wooden pieces decorated with unique facial expressions
Pegs make pieces easily connectable and stackable
Grasping the pieces and putting them together can encourage fine motor skills
Figuring out how to connect and stack the pieces can foster logical thinking and problem solving
Using the pieces and accessories to build unique totem towers can inspire imagination and creativity
The different colors and textures provide a stimulating visual and tactile playtime experience

column6: Wooden Toys Deep Blue Sea Stacker
column7: Designed to foster physical and cognitive development in toddlers, this unique stacking toy features lights, sounds, and games that are meant to encourage fine motor skills, logical thinking, problem solving, curiosity, and discovery.
column8:
They say there are plenty of fish in the seaand theyre right! But there are also plenty of crabs, turtles, snails, and other critters that live beneath the waves. At Fisher-Price, we like to imagine these sea-dwellers do a lot of socializingparties, line dancing, barbecues, and, of course, games. (Okay, maybe not too many barbecues.) The Deep Blue Sea Stacker, from the Fisher-Price Wooden Toys collection, lets children take part in a variety of games featuring nine adorable play pieces designed to look like different underwater animals. With lights, sounds, and four modes of play, the Deep Blue Sea Stacker is more than a stacking toy; its an interactive playtime experience created to help foster physical and cognitive development. Each mode focuses on a different way to play by encouraging recognition of colors, shapes, and numbers through matching, stacking, and counting as children place the play pieces on the correct poles. To make sure children receive plenty of visual, auditory, and tactile stimulation, the toy features lots of music, sound effects, colored lights, and a gorgeous beech wood design to tie it all together. Contemporary meets classic with tried-and-true developmental play (stacking and matching), a modern aesthetic, and unique, fun-filled electronic content that helps guide children through different games, all of which are meant to encourage fine motor skills, logical thinking, problem solving, curiosity, and discovery. Deep sea adventures have never been more accessible. Whether your child is an aspiring oceanographer, or just loves playing with lights, sounds, and adorable animals, the Deep Blue Sea Stacker brings a world of fun, beneficial play to the surface.

Unique sea-inspired stacking toy is made with real beech wood
Includes 9 play pieces designed to look like a variety of sea creatures
Stack the sea creatures by placing them on the correct poles
The shapes of the sea creatures correspond to the shapes of the 3 different polescircle, square, triangle
4 modes of play encourage recognition of shapes, colors, and numbers
Different modes feature lights, sounds, phrases, and music

Give these fun jewel-crazy characters a spin, with gravity-defying action to amaze little ones!
column8:
What are YOs and what makes them go? Theyre cool, round things that love to spin fast, and love to spin slow. How do they stay on track? kids ask as they play. Its magic of course! (Thats what you should say.) Just place the Jewely-YOs on the YO-Rail track piece for on-the-go play. Then take the YOs for a ridemake em slidego upside downand round & round & round! Its a whole new spin on defying gravity!

Theres a crazy bejewelled character on one side of each YO, and a cool optical effect on the other side. The YO-Rail track piece also attaches to the Spinnyos Giant YO-ller Coaster and H2YO Splash Park sets for more spin-tacular fun! (Coaster and Splash Park sold separately.) How do YOs stay on the YO-Rail track?

Well, it seems like magic, but actually theres a kid-safe magnetic axle inside the YOs that attaches to the metallic edge on the track. Theyre so much fun that once kids start spinning em, they wont want to stop! (You wont either try em and see for yourself!) Theyre YO-tally awesome!

Place the Spinnyos Jewely-YO Duo on the YO-Rail track piece and move it in any direction to send the YOs spinning up, down and all around!
Wacky girl character on one side, cool visual effect on the other
Includes 2 YOs and 1 YO-Rail track piece that attaches to the Spinnyos Giant YO-ller Coaster and H2YO Splash Park sets (sold separately)
Discover the YO-tally wacky world of Spinnyos toys! Collect all the YOs in different fun themes! (Each sold separately and subject to availability)
Perfect toy for on-the-go play!

A turtle has the ability to hide his limbs and head when hes scared, but your child can bring the Shape-imals Turtle out of his shell literally. When children use their little fingers to open the turtles little arms and head, theyre engaging in play that promotes fine motor skills and fosters logical thinking and problem solving. Plus, the shape of this turtles circular beech wood body is no accidentthe entire Shape-imals collection is designed to help encourage shape recognition. If only all geometry could be this adorable.

column7: 4-in-1 grows with your little one  and the dishwasher-safe seat, tray & tray insert make clean-ups easy-peasy!
column8:
This versatile high chair can juggle all kinds of functions with ease, just like a new parent. Its a full-size high chair with recline a removable SpaceSaver high chair that fits most dining chairs a toddler booster to bring little ones to the big kid table and a youth chair thats easy to roll into place! You can even use it with two kids at once - seat one child in the youth seat and another in either the SpaceSaver high chair or booster seat!

Clean-up is a breeze. The seat, tray & tray insert come apart and go right in the dishwasher, so getting them totally clean is totally easy. With no crumb-catching crevices, the stain-resistant seat pad wipes down in no time and pops right into the washing machine. And if your messy little one needs a quick once-over, just pull out a baby wipe from the container right on the chair. With conveniences like an easy-fold frame for stowing or going and one-hand tray removal, the Fisher-Price 4-in-1 Total Clean High Chair is sure to be a busy moms new BFF!

4 products in 1!
1. Full-Size High Chair With 6-position height adjustment & 3-position recline to get the right fit!
2. SpaceSaver High Chair Fits most dining chairs great for home or on the go!
3. Toddler Booster A great pick-me-up for the big kid table4. Youth Seat Easy to roll into place & easy to fold to save space!
SpaceSaver High Chair easily comes apart so you can place each piece in the dishwasher for quick & easy clean-up!
Baby wipes storage is right at hand for spills and messy babies
Look, ma, no crumbs! Stain-resistant, crevice-free seat pad wipes down easily and is machine washable
EZ Clean straps just wipe clean
Only one free hand? No problem with one-hand tray removal
High chair frame folds in half making it easy to stow or take on the go!
Tray & tray insert store in a snap to the back of the frame
4 wheels for easy rollin

column7: Packed with more than 40 flaps, Little People Lets Go to the Zoo!
column8:
takes kids on a learning adventure. Eddie, Sarah Lynn, and their friends discover colors, animal sounds, counting and more as they enjoy a trip to the town zoo. With so much to discover, this book will be one kids will want to open again and again!

column6: Little People Big Adventure Wood Puzzle-Castle
column8:
The series of 12 piece wood puzzles features Fisher-Price Little People in four adventure themes; Pet Shop, Dinosaur Cove, Pirate Ship and Castle. Each puzzle contains 12 large, easy to grasp wooden pieces. Wooden storage tray makes cleanup after play, easy and fun.

Each puzzle develops fine motor skills, problem solving and imagination.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People Mix & Match Wood Puzzle-Eddie
column8:
Mix and Match different outfits with Eddie. What outfit will Eddie wear today? Each set includes 12 pieces: 5 tops, 5 bottoms and 2 different faces to create lots of unique and silly dress-up looks. Everything fits inside in a wooden box for easy cleanup and storage.

Each puzzle develops Imagination, self-expression and gross motor skills.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People All Aboard Numbers Learning Train
column8:
This colorful train puzzle is over 3 feet long and includes 30 extra large pieces. Colorful circus animals help young puzzlers learn to count from 1-10.

Each puzzle develops number recognition, fine motor skills and problem solving.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People World of Wheelies  Activity Floor Puzzle-Farm
column7: Puzzles and vehicles combine to create a new world of fun.
column8:
Zoom your Little People Wheelies vehicles over the completed floor puzzle. Each of the puzzles comes with its own unique vehicle, has 24 extra large pieces and is over two feet tall! Collect all 3 puzzles to create your one gigantic Wheelies world!

Farm floor puzzle includes Tractor.

Each puzzle develops fine motor skills, problem solving and imagination.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People Discover & Learn Chunky Wood Puzzle-Farm
column8:
Discover hidden surprises under each of the 7 chunky wooden puzzle pieces. What is in the Barn? The only way to find out is to take out the pieces and put them in again and again. Matching pieces to appropriate shapes helps little ones learn shape and animal recognition.

Each puzzle develops fine motor skills, problem solving and imagination.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People All Aboard Alphabet Learning Train
column8:
This colorful train puzzle is over 3 feet long and includes 30 extra large pieces. All aboard as you join the exotic animals on the circus train that teaches the 26 letters of the alphabet.

Each puzzle develops alphabet recognition, fine motor skills and problem solving.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People ABC Puzzle Block Set
column8:
The Little People ABC Puzzle Block Set includes 30 classic wood blocks, with four sides of play, that teach upper and lower case letters, basic shapes and beginner words. The blocks also fit together to form a challenging farm scene puzzle!

All the blocks store in the convenient tray for easy clean up.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column7: The Deluxe Wide Opening Diaper Bag features frame construction that opens extra wideand stays open!
column8:
Featuring the FastFinder Pocket System, all of your key items are at arms reach on the exterior of the bag with easy-to-find labels. The insulated bottles pocket keeps bottles cold. The exterior wipes case can be accessed with a press of a button, so you can grab a wipe with one hand and hold onto baby with the other! The pacifier pocket can be easily wiped clean. And the diapers pocket is large enough for multiple changes. The labels also help secondary users locate and replace these essentials so theyre sure to be just where you left themso youll have what you need when baby needs it!

Frame construction opens extra wide and stays open.
Nylon twill construction and printed nylon lining.

One insulated zippered bottle pocket.
Exterior wipes pocket includes wipes case that can be accessed without removing it from the bag.
Six interior nylon pockets to help organize your everyday items like childrens cups, snacks, creams, and a change of clothes.
Can be carried using the adjustable shoulder strap with padded strap cover, or easy-to-grab top handles with strap cover.
Includes a cushioned changing pad and a baby wipe case.
Four plastic feet to help keep the bottom of your bag clean.

column6: Laugh & Learn Apptivity Case for iPad Devices (Red)
Laugh & Learn Apptivity Case for iPad Devices (Pink)
My Little Lamb Cradle n Swing
column8:
Sometimes your little one likes being held over your shoulder. Sometimes on your knee. Other times, she wants to be cradled in your arms as you rock her side-to-side or back-and-forth. But for the times you need to put baby down, heres a swing that cradles and swings, soothes and entertains her just the way she likes it! It surrounds her in plush, cozy fabrics and a canopy that cocoons her. The soothing continues with eight tunes and a side-to-side cradle motion, a lot like the way you rock her in your arms. When your little lamb is ready for play, the swinging changes to a back-and-forth motion (because babies love variety) and shes engaged with nature sound tracks and a mobile featuring a mirror, floating clouds and little lambs to entertain her. Includes six soothing swing speeds, little plush friend tethered right to the removable tray, and bead bar. Sturdy steel frame has legs that fold in for storage and portability. Requires 4 D batteries.

Weight Limit: 25 lbs. (11.3 kg)

Developmental Guidelines: Use cradle swing from birth until a child becomes active and can climb out of the seat.

Sensory
Motorized mobile with soft lambs & puffy clouds spins gently overhead; mirrored globe lets baby see all around!

Two ways to swing! Easily converts from side-to-side cradle swing to traditional head-to-toe swinging motion.
Customizable! Choose swinging, or any combination of swinging, music & mobile
3-position seat, 2-position recline
Removable tray with bead bar & plush lamb rattle toy
